Slices & Spritzers Pizzeria Online Menu

üçï Project Overview

This is a single-page web application designed as a modern, responsive online menu and ordering interface for a fictional pizzeria, "Slices & Spritzers."

The application focuses on demonstrating frontend functionality, including a working shopping cart with real-time tax calculation.

‚ú® Key Features

Fully Responsive Design: Optimized for seamless viewing and interaction across mobile, tablet, and desktop devices using Tailwind CSS.

Interactive Menu: Displays signature pizza items with dedicated "Add to Cart" functionality.

Sliding Shopping Cart: A responsive side modal displays cart contents, subtotal, taxes, and the final order total.

Real-time Tax Calculation: The JavaScript logic accurately applies the Ontario Harmonized Sales Tax (HST) of 13% to the subtotal before calculating the final total.

Cart Management: Users can add multiple items and remove individual items directly from the cart.

Smooth Navigation: Scroll links ensure a smooth user experience when navigating between sections.

