üöÄ Getting Started

Since this is a single, self-contained HTML file, running the project is straightforward:

Clone the repository (once uploaded to GitHub) or download the pizza_place.html file.

Open the file (pizza_place.html) directly in any modern web browser.

The application requires no backend, server, or build step. All necessary scripts (Tailwind CSS, Font Awesome, and custom JavaScript) are included directly within the file.

üí∞ Tax Logic

The JavaScript code includes a constant for the Ontario HST rate and applies it to the cart's subtotal in the updateCartUI function:

// Define the tax rate for Ontario (13% HST)
const ONTARIO_HST_RATE = 0.13;

// ... inside updateCartUI function
const tax = subtotal * ONTARIO_HST_RATE;
const finalTotal = subtotal + tax;


This ensures all prices displayed in the final total are inclusive of the mandatory provincial tax.
